title: Freaky Friday Tank, T.K. Kirkland and More
itunes:title: Freaky Friday Tank, T.K. Kirkland and More
description:
Today on the show we had Tank join us after coming off of an interesting week as he discuss not only his new album... but, his recent controversy and confusion from his recent Lip Service interview. T.K. Kirkland also stopped by to discuss his new comedy and masculine fashion. Moreover, Donkey of the Day went to a man in Florida who has a problem humping stuffed Disney animals.
